The paper deals with the capacity of networks, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). It also discusses the modeling of networks and the use of computational tools, which are relevant to network science (cs.NI) and systems and control (cs.SI). The paper also introduces upper and lower bounding models, which are related to optimization and approximation algorithms (cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses the use of network coding, which is a topic in computer communication (cs.CC).
